org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.chromium.debug.core.model

Class ConsolePseudoProcess

  • java.lang.Object
    • PlatformObject
      • org.eclipse.wst.jsdt.chromium.debug.core.model.ConsolePseudoProcess

  • public class ConsolePseudoProcess
extends PlatformObject
    This process corresponds to a Debugger-Chrome connection and its main purpose is to expose connection log (see process console in UI).
